\c 26
\s Dhavhidhi anokumbira kuti Jehovha amururamisire
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Nditongerei Jehovha, nokuti ndakafamba nokusanyengera kwangu; Ndakavimbawo naJehovha handitedzemuki.
\v 2 Ndinzverei Jehovha, ndiidzei, Natsai itsvo dzangu nomoyo wangu.
\v 3 Nokuti unyoro bwenyu huri pamberi pameso angu, Ndakafamba muchokwadi chenyu.
\v 4 Handina kugara navanhu venhema, Handingafambidzani navanyepedzeri.
\v 5 Ndinovenga ungano yavanoita zvakaipa, Handingagari navatadzi.
\v 6 Ndichashambidza maoko angu ndisina mhosva; Ndigopoteredza aritari yenyu saizvozvo, Jehovha.
\v 7 Kuti ndiparidze nenzwi rokuvonga, Ndiudze vanhu zvamabasa enyu ose anoshamisa.
\v 8 Jehovha, ndinoda hugaro bweimba yenyu, Nenzvimbo panogara kubwinya kwenyu.
\v 9 Regai kusanganisa mweya wangu pamwechete navatadzi, Noupenyu hwangu navateuri veropa;
\v 10 Vakabata zvakashata pamaoko avo, Ruoko rwavo rworudyi ruzere nefufuro.
\v 11 Asi kana ndirini ndichafamba nokusanyengera kwangu; Ndidzikunurei, mundinzwire tsitsi.
\v 12 Rutsoka rwangu rumire pakati chechetere; Ndicharumbidza Jehovha paungano
